quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  104,1,"shr whlak likuli mghtab llnas, tean fyhm"
  104,2,aldhy kan hmmuh jame almal wtedadh
  104,3,"yzn 'anah damin linafsih bhdha almal aldhy jmeh, alkhulud fi aldunya wal'iflat min alhsab"
  104,4,"lys al'amr kama zn, lyutrhnn fi alnaar alati thshm kl ma yulqa fyha"
  104,5,wma 'adrak -ayha alrswl- ma hqyqt alnar?
  104,6,'inha nar allah almuqadat alty min shdtha tnfudh min al'ajsam 'iilaa alqlwb
  104,7,'inha nar allah almuqadat alty min shdtha tnfudh min al'ajsam 'iilaa alqlwb
  104,8,'iinaha ealayhim mtbaqt fi salasil waghlal mtwwalt; lialaa yakhrujuu mnha
  104,9,'inha ealayhim mtbaqt fi salasil waghlal mtwwalt; lialaa yakhrujuu mnha